    <img src="https://www.animatedimages.org/data/media/1664/animated-work-in-progress-image-0020.gif" alt="Under Construction" class="construction">
    <span class="blink" style="font-size: 1.2em; color: red; font-weight: bold;"> SITE UNDER CONSTRUCTION!!! </span>
